DOC.brief_summary: This is an open-label, randomized, two-way crossover study to evaluate the steady-state effect of fesoterodine (8 mg QD) on the pharmacodynamics and pharmacokinetics of a single supratherapeutic dose of warfarin (25 mg) in healthy subjects.
DOC.brief_title: The Effect Of Fesoterodine On Pharmacokinetics And Pharmacodynamics Of Warfarin In Healthy Subjects
DOC.criteria: Healthy male and/or female subjects between the ages of 18 and 55 years Not healthy subjectssubjects with acute or chronic medical or psychiatric conditions or laboratory abnormality
